1.How to identify wheteher the problem is of heap?
-> whenever in qus k is given and smallest/largest is given it is heap problem
ie>> k+(smallest/largest)=heap
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.a k + smallest --> MAXHEAP
  b k + largest  --> MINHEAP
a) we need to find kth smallest ie we need to eliminate maxium so use maxheap
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
sorting->nlogn   
k is given nlogk
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Largest,Greatest,Top->MINHEAP
smallest,lowest,closest-->MAXHEAP